# Publish RAG corpus PDFs used by chatbot retrieval while keeping other PDFs ignored.
!Models/Uruti chatbot/
!Models/Uruti chatbot/uruti_rag_corpus/
!Models/Uruti chatbot/uruti_rag_corpus/pdfs/
